# Expense Write Off Direct Exposure Property Commercial Retail Amount

## identifier
de8721

## type
float

## definition
This is the amount written off directly to Profit & Loss of the value of the reporting party's investments that result in an exposure to the asset class of commercial retail property.
     
Commercial retail property exposure is defined according to the nature of the risk. An exposure should be classified as commercial retail property risk, if the exposure is subject to the performance of the commercial retail property market. This exposure does not include property used for the reporting party's own operational use.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Expense.WriteOffDirectExposurePropertyCommercialRetail.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpr/bafpr1.02.06
- period=duration
